Use Expo managed workflow conventions for this project.

Read package.json, app.json, tsconfig.json, and database.ts before changing behavior.

Keep edits small and preserve MyBrain AI task-state semantics: pending, frozen, completed.

Treat database.ts as the local SQLite core. Prefer typed helpers and read-only checks.

When adding native dependencies, verify Expo compatibility first and keep Babel in sync.

Use ASCII unless a file already requires another character set.

Do not claim encryption, sync, or background-device support unless code actually implements it.
